cdiv dir\\\\u003d\\\\\\\"auto\\\\\\\"\\\\u003e\\\\u003cdiv dir\\\\u003d\\\\\\\"auto\\\\\\\"\\\\u003eCrie o design de um site institucional Premium, elegante e minimalista para uma empresa de eventos de alto padrão chamada \\\\u0026quot;Adriana Almeida | Buffet, Cerimonial e Assessoria\\\\u0026quot;. \\\\u003c/div\\\\u003e\\\\u003cdiv dir\\\\u003d\\\\\\\"auto\\\\\\\"\\\\u003e\\\\u003cbr\\\\u003e\\\\u003c/div\\\\u003e\\\\u003cdiv dir\\\\u003d\\\\\\\"auto\\\\\\\"\\\\u003eO design deve ser moderno, responsivo (mobile-friendly) e focado em conversão, utilizando uma paleta de cores baseada em Preto Absoluto, Dourado Metálico e detalhes em Vermelho Sofisticado para botões de ação (CTAs). Use fontes serifadas elegantes para os títulos e fontes sem serifa modernas e limpas para os textos de leitura.\\\\u003c/div\\\\u003e\\\\u003cdiv dir\\\\u003d\\\\\\\"auto\\\\\\\"\\\\u003e\\\\u003cbr\\\\u003e\\\\u003c/div\\\\u003e\\\\u003cdiv dir\\\\u003d\\\\\\\"auto\\\\\\\"\\\\u003eEstruture o site em uma única página (Single Page Application) com as seguintes seções essenciais:\\\\u003c/div\\\\u003e\\\\u003cdiv dir\\\\u003d\\\\\\\"auto\\\\\\\"\\\\u003e\\\\u003cbr\\\\u003e\\\\u003c/div\\\\u003e\\\\u003cdiv dir\\\\u003d\\\\\\\"auto\\\\\\\"\\\\u003e1. HERO SECTION (Abertura do Site):\\\\u003c/div\\\\u003e\\\\u003cdiv dir\\\\u003d\\\\\\\"auto\\\\\\\"\\\\u003e- Logotipo destacado no topo: \\\\u0026quot;Adriana Almeida\\\\u0026quot; com o subtítulo \\\\u0026quot;Buffet, Cerimonial e Assessoria\\\\u0026quot; em letras douradas sobre fundo preto.\\\\u003c/div\\\\u003e\\\\u003cdiv dir\\\\u003d\\\\\\\"auto\\\\\\\"\\\\u003e- Imagem de fundo ou banner em carrossel de alta qualidade mostrando um casamento sofisticado (noiva e noivo) e uma mesa de buffet de luxo.\\\\u003c/div\\\\u003e\\\\u003cdiv dir\\\\u003d\\\\\\\"auto\\\\\\\"\\\\u003e- Frase de impacto principal (Headline) e um botão de ação destacado em vermelho: \\\\u0026quot;Solicitar Orçamento Gratuito\\\\u0026quot;.\\\\u003c/div\\\\u003e\\\\u003cdiv dir\\\\u003d\\\\\\\"auto\\\\\\\"\\\\u003e\\\\u003cbr\\\\u003e\\\\u003c/div\\\\u003e\\\\u003cdiv dir\\\\u003d\\\\\\\"auto\\\\\\\"\\\\u003e2. NOSSOS SERVIÇOS (Galeria Visual com Imagens Reais):\\\\u003c/div\\\\u003e\\\\u003cdiv dir\\\\u003d\\\\\\\"auto\\\\\\\"\\\\u003eCrie um grid ou carrossel de cartões elegantes. Cada serviço deve ter uma imagem de alta qualidade correspondente e um título em dourado. Corrija a escrita dos itens para:\\\\u003c/div\\\\u003e\\\\u003cdiv dir\\\\u003d\\\\\\\"auto\\\\\\\"\\\\u003e- Casamentos\\\\u003c/div\\\\u003e\\\\u003cdiv dir\\\\u003d\\\\\\\"auto\\\\\\\"\\\\u003e- Formaturas\\\\u003c/div\\\\u003e\\\\u003cdiv dir\\\\u003d\\\\\\\"auto\\\\\\\"\\\\u003e- Eventos Corporativos\\\\u003c/div\\\\u003e\\\\u003cdiv dir\\\\u003d\\\\\\\"auto\\\\\\\"\\\\u003e- Coffee Break\\\\u003c/div\\\\u003e\\\\u003cdiv dir\\\\u003d\\\\\\\"auto\\\\\\\"\\\\u003e- Aniversários e Confraternizações\\\\u003c/div\\\\u003e\\\\u003cdiv dir\\\\u003d\\\\\\\"auto\\\\\\\"\\\\u003e- Batizados, Chás de Bebê e Chás Revelação\\\\u003c/div\\\\u003e\\\\u003cdiv dir\\\\u003d\\\\\\\"auto\\\\\\\"\\\\u003e\\\\u003cbr\\\\u003e\\\\u003c/div\\\\u003e\\\\u003cdiv dir\\\\u003d\\\\\\\"auto\\\\\\\"\\\\u003e3. DEPOIMENTOS DE CLIENTES (Prova Social):\\\\u003c/div\\\\u003e\\\\u003cdiv dir\\\\u003d\\\\\\\"auto\\\\\\\"\\\\u003e- Uma seção elegante com fundo escuro ou dourado suave para exibir avaliações e comentários reais de clientes satisfeitos que contrataram a Adriana Almeida, reforçando a autoridade e confiança da marca.\\\\u003c/div\\\\u003e\\\\u003cdiv dir\\\\u003d\\\\\\\"auto\\\\\\\"\\\\u003e\\\\u003cbr\\\\u003e\\\\u003c/div\\\\u003e\\\\u003cdiv dir\\\\u003d\\\\\\\"auto\\\\\\\"\\\\u003e4. SEÇÃO DE ORÇAMENTO (Formulário de Captação):\\\\u003c/div\\\\u003e\\\\u003cdiv dir\\\\u003d\\\\\\\"auto\\\\\\\"\\\\u003eUm formulário limpo e direto com o título \\\\u0026quot;Faça seu Orçamento Sem Compromisso\\\\u0026quot;. O formulário deve conter apenas 4 campos:\\\\u003c/div\\\\u003e\\\\u003